snippet.title: GODDESS OF VICTORY: NIKKE | Evangelion Collaboration | Into The Infinite 2024
snippet.description:
Step into the sci-fi world of GODDESS OF VICTORY: NIKKE, an RPG shooter where you lead a squad of anime maidens, each armed with unique sci-fi weaponry. This month, experience a special crossover as characters from the iconic anime Neon Genesis Evangelion join the fray, becoming playable characters in Nikke's universe. Developed by Shift Up.

Play now: www.nikke-en.com/
